        "type": "message",
        "text": "Is \"waste of their time and expertise\" a problem because of cost\/opportunity cost, or is the concern that it would annoy the SME?  If it's the latter, my experience (personally and running a business entirely dedicated to enlisting SMEs to write expert content) is that a lot of SMEs are perfectly content to write about basics in their field, explaining concepts to outsiders\/newbies.",
